#: ../../content/facturation/application-supplements.md:192
msgid ""
"Supplements reporting on the graph view, one bar per resident with the "
"billed amount"
msgstr ""
"Rapportering van de supplementen in grafiekweergave, één balk per bewoner "
"met het gefactureerde bedrag"

#: ../../content/facturation/application-supplements.md:194
msgid "After generation only"
msgstr "Pas na generatie"

#: ../../content/facturation/application-supplements.md:197
msgid ""
"Supplements only appear in the reporting once the **billing period is "
"generated** for the relevant month."
msgstr ""
"De supplementen verschijnen pas in de rapportage zodra de "
"**facturatieperiode gegenereerd** is voor de betrokken maand."

#: ../../content/facturation/application-supplements.md:201
msgid "Key points to remember"
msgstr "Kernpunten om te onthouden"

#: ../../content/facturation/application-supplements.md:203
msgid ""
"The **Supplements** app is a dedicated entry screen; it acts on the **same "
"envelopes and conventions** as billing — no duplicate data."
msgstr ""
"De app **Supplementen** is een speciaal invoerscherm; ze werkt op **dezelfde"
" enveloppes en conventies** als de facturatie — geen dubbele gegevens."

#: ../../content/facturation/application-supplements.md:205
msgid ""
"The **Residents** screen is the starting point: click a resident to open "
"their catalog, or **select several** (Ctrl+click / long press / **Multiple "
"selection**) then **Supplements (N)** to serve them all at once."
msgstr ""
"Het scherm **Bewoners** is het vertrekpunt: klik op een bewoner om zijn "
"catalogus te openen, of **selecteer er meerdere** (Ctrl+klik / lang "
"indrukken / **Meervoudige selectie**) en dan **Supplementen (N)** om ze in "
"één keer te bedienen."

#: ../../content/facturation/application-supplements.md:208
msgid ""
"**One-off** = once on the envelope; **convention** = recurring, on the "
"resident, surviving stay changes."
msgstr ""
"**Eenmalig** = één keer op de enveloppe; **conventie** = terugkerend, op de "
"bewoner, bestand tegen verblijfswijzigingen."

#: ../../content/facturation/application-supplements.md:210
msgid "A product under an **active convention** cannot be entered as one-off."
msgstr "Een product onder **actieve conventie** voert u niet eenmalig in."

#: ../../content/facturation/application-supplements.md:211
msgid ""
"The **catalog** carries the type and the price (value specific to the "
"facility); the **reporting** tracks amounts per resident, product and month."
msgstr ""
"De **catalogus** draagt het type en de prijs (waarde eigen aan de "
"instelling); de **rapportage** volgt de bedragen per bewoner, product en "
"maand."

